\c 12
\s UMiriyamu loAroni baphikisana loMozisi
\p
\v 1 UMiriyamu loAroni basebekhuluma bemelene loMozisi ngenxa yowesifazana umEthiyophiyakazi owayemthethe, ngoba wayethethe umfazi umEthiyophiyakazi\x + Eks. 2.21.\x*.
\v 2 Basebesithi: Kambe, iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulume ngoMozisi kuphela? Kayikhulumanga langathi?\x + Eks. 4.15; 7.1,2; 15.20. Mika 6.4.\x* LeN\nd kosi\nd* yakuzwa\x + Gen. 29.33. Nani 11.1; 2 Kho. 19.4. Isa. 37.4. Hez. 35.12,13.\x*.
\v 3 Njalo indoda uMozisi yayimnene kakhulu kulabo bonke abantu abaphezu kobuso bomhlaba\x + Hlab. 76.9.\x*.
\v 4 Khona iN\nd kosi\nd* yahle yathi kuMozisi lakuAroni lakuMiriyamu: Phumani lobathathu lize ethenteni lenhlangano. Baphuma-ke bona bobathathu\x + Hlab. 76.9.\x*.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisehla isensikeni yeyezi, yema emnyango wethente, yabiza uAroni loMiriyamu; basebephuma bobabili\x + 11.25; 16.19.\x*.
\v 6 Yasisithi: Zwanini-ke amazwi ami; uba kukhona umprofethi \add phakathi\add* kwenu, mina iN\nd kosi\nd* ngizaziveza kuye ngombono\x + Gen. 46.2. Hez. 1.1. Dan. 10.8,16. Gen. 15.1. Dan. 8.2. Luka 1.11,22. Seb. 10.11,17. 22.17,18.\x*, ngikhulume laye ngephupho\x + Gen. 31.10,11. 1 Kho. 3.5. Jobe 33.15. Mat. 1.20.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa inceku yami uMozisi kanjalo\x + Hlab. 105.26.\x*, uthembekile\x + Heb. 3.2,5.\x* endlini yami yonke\x + 1 Tim. 3.15.\x*.
\v 8 Ngikhuluma laye umlomo ngomlomo\x + Eks. 33.11. Nani 7.89. Dute. 34.10; 1 Kor. 13.12.\x*, langokubona, kungeyisikho ngemizekeliso\x + Hlu. 14.12; Hlab. 49.4; 78.2. Zaga 1.6.\x*; futhi ukhangela isimo seN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 33.19.\x*\nd*. Ngakho kungani belingesabi ukukhuluma limelene lenceku yami uMozisi?\x + 12.7.\x*
\v 9 Njalo ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwabavuthela; yasihamba.
\v 10 Kwathi lapho iyezi lisuka phezu kwethente, khangela, uMiriyamu\x + Dute. 24.9.\x* wayelobulephero\x + 2 Kho. 5.27. Levi 13.10; 2 Kho. 15.5; 2 Lan. 26.19,20.\x*, \add emhlophe\add* njengeliqhwa elikhithikileyo. UAroni wasemkhangela uMiriyamu, khangela-ke, ulobulephero.
\v 11 UAroni wasesithi kuMozisi: Hawu nkosi yami, akungabeki isono phezu kwethu, okungaso senze ngobuthutha, lokungaso sonile\x + 2 Sam. 19.19; 24.10. Zaga 30.32.\x*.
\v 12 Ake angabi njengofileyo, othi nxa ephuma esiswini sikanina ingxenye yenyama yakhe idliwe.
\v 13 UMozisi wasekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni esithi: Nkulunkulu, ake umelaphe, ngiyakuncenga.
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Uba uyise ubemkhafulele lokumkhafulela ngamathe ebusweni bakhe\x + Dute. 25.9. Jobe 30.10.\x*, ubengayikuyangeka insuku eziyisikhombisa yini? Kavalelwe ngaphandle kwenkamba insuku eziyisikhombisa\x + Levi 13.46.\x*; lemva kwalokho emukelwe.
\v 15 UMiriyamu wasevalelwa ngaphandle kwenkamba insuku eziyisikhombisa; labantu kabasukanga, waze wemukelwa uMiriyamu\x + 2 Lan. 26.20,21. Luka 17.12.\x*.
\v 16 Lemva kwalokho abantu basuka eHazerothi\x + 11.35; 33.18.\x*, bamisa inkamba enkangala yeParani\x + Gen. 21.21. Nani 10.12; 13.3,26. 1 Sam. 25.1.\x*.